## 3. 도메인 2: 음성 통화/세션

### JPA Entity (통화 이력 - MySQL 저장용)

파일 위치: `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/call/`

```kotlin
// VoiceRoomEntity.kt  -- 통화방 메타 (MySQL)
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "maum", name = "voice_room")
@EntityListeners(AuditingEntityListener::class)
class VoiceRoomEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    val hostUserId: String,                       // 방 개설자
    var title: String? = null,                    // 방 제목 (공개방)
    var roomType: Int = 0,                        // 0: 1:1 매칭, 1: 공개방
    var maxParticipants: Int = 2,                 // 최대 참여 인원
    var currentParticipants: Int = 0,

    @Enumerated(EnumType.STRING)
    var roomStatus: RoomStatus = RoomStatus.WAITING,

    var startedAt: LocalDateTime? = null,
    var endedAt: LocalDateTime? = null,

    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @LastModifiedDate
    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
)

enum class RoomStatus { WAITING, ACTIVE, ENDED }
```

```kotlin
// VoiceSessionEntity.kt  -- 개별 참여 세션 이력 (MySQL)
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "maum", name = "voice_session")
@EntityListeners(AuditingEntityListener::class)
class VoiceSessionEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    val roomId: String,                           // FK -> voice_room.id
    val userId: String,                           // 참여자
    var joinedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
    var leftAt: LocalDateTime? = null,
    var durationSeconds: Int = 0,                 // 통화 시간 (초)

    @Enumerated(EnumType.STRING)
    var sessionStatus: SessionStatus = SessionStatus.JOINED,

    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @LastModifiedDate
    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
)

enum class SessionStatus { JOINED, LEFT, DISCONNECTED }
```

### Redis 구조 (활성 세션 실시간 상태)

```
# 활성 통화방 상태
Key: "voice:room:{roomId}"
Type: Hash
Fields:
  hostUserId: String
  roomStatus: "WAITING" | "ACTIVE" | "ENDED"
  currentParticipants: Int
  startedAt: Timestamp
TTL: 2시간 (통화 최대 지속 시간)

# 참여자 목록
Key: "voice:room:{roomId}:participants"
Type: Set
Members: userId
TTL: 2시간

# 유저 현재 참여 방
Key: "voice:user:{userId}:currentRoom"
Type: String
Value: roomId
TTL: 2시간
```

### DynamoDB 구조 (통화 이벤트 로그)

```
Table: voice_call_event_log

Partition Key: userId (String)
Sort Key: eventAt (String, ISO8601)

Attributes:
  roomId: String
  eventType: "JOIN" | "LEAVE" | "MUTE" | "UNMUTE" | "DISCONNECT"
  durationSeconds: Number (LEFT/DISCONNECT 시)
  createdAt: String

GSI-1: roomId-eventAt-index
  Partition Key: roomId
  Sort Key: eventAt
  (용도: 특정 방의 전체 이벤트 조회)
```

### 인덱스 전략

```sql
-- voice_room 테이블
CREATE INDEX idx_room_host ON maum.voice_room (host_user_id, room_status);
CREATE INDEX idx_room_status_created ON maum.voice_room (room_status, created_at);

-- voice_session 테이블
CREATE INDEX idx_session_room ON maum.voice_session (room_id, session_status);
CREATE INDEX idx_session_user ON maum.voice_session (user_id, joined_at);
CREATE INDEX idx_session_user_room ON maum.voice_session (user_id, room_id); -- 중복 참여 방지
```

### GraphQL 스키마

파일 위치: `graphql/src/main/resources/graphql/call.graphqls`

```graphql
type VoiceRoom {
    id: ID!
    hostUserId: ID!
    title: String
    roomType: Int!
    maxParticipants: Int!
    currentParticipants: Int!
    roomStatus: String!
    participants: [SimpleUser!]!
    startedAt: String
    endedAt: String
    createdAt: String!
}

type VoiceSession {
    id: ID!
    roomId: ID!
    userId: ID!
    joinedAt: String!
    leftAt: String
    durationSeconds: Int!
    sessionStatus: String!
}

type SimpleUser {
    id: ID!
    nickname: String!
    profileImageUrl: String
    mannerScore: Int!
}

input CreateVoiceRoomInput {
    title: String
    roomType: Int!
    maxParticipants: Int!
}

extend type Query {
    voiceRoom(roomId: ID!): VoiceRoom
    activeVoiceRooms(limit: Int, offset: Int): [VoiceRoom!]!
    myCallHistory(limit: Int, offset: Int): [VoiceSession!]!
}

extend type Mutation {
    createVoiceRoom(input: CreateVoiceRoomInput!): VoiceRoom!
    joinVoiceRoom(roomId: ID!): VoiceRoom!
    leaveVoiceRoom(roomId: ID!): Boolean!
}
```

### gRPC Proto

파일 위치: `protobuf/src/main/proto/call/call_service.proto`

```protobuf
syntax = "proto3";
package call;

option java_multiple_files = true;
option java_package = "com.maum.backend.protobuf.call";

service CallService {
  rpc CreateVoiceRoom(CreateVoiceRoomRequest) returns (CreateVoiceRoomResponse);
  rpc JoinVoiceRoom(JoinVoiceRoomRequest) returns (JoinVoiceRoomResponse);
  rpc LeaveVoiceRoom(LeaveVoiceRoomRequest) returns (LeaveVoiceRoomResponse);
  rpc GetVoiceRoom(GetVoiceRoomRequest) returns (GetVoiceRoomResponse);
  rpc ListActiveRooms(ListActiveRoomsRequest) returns (ListActiveRoomsResponse);
  rpc GetCallHistory(GetCallHistoryRequest) returns (GetCallHistoryResponse);
}

message VoiceRoomProto {
  string id = 1;
  string host_user_id = 2;
  optional string title = 3;
  int32 room_type = 4;
  int32 max_participants = 5;
  int32 current_participants = 6;
  string room_status = 7;
  optional string started_at = 8;
  optional string ended_at = 9;
  string created_at = 10;
}

message CreateVoiceRoomRequest {
  string user_id = 1;
  optional string title = 2;
  int32 room_type = 3;
  int32 max_participants = 4;
}

message CreateVoiceRoomResponse {
  VoiceRoomProto room = 1;
}

message JoinVoiceRoomRequest {
  string user_id = 1;
  string room_id = 2;
}

message JoinVoiceRoomResponse {
  VoiceRoomProto room = 1;
  string session_id = 2;
}

message LeaveVoiceRoomRequest {
  string user_id = 1;
  string room_id = 2;
  string session_id = 3;
}

message LeaveVoiceRoomResponse {
  bool success = 1;
  int32 duration_seconds = 2;
}

message GetVoiceRoomRequest {
  string room_id = 1;
}

message GetVoiceRoomResponse {
  VoiceRoomProto room = 1;
}

message ListActiveRoomsRequest {
  int32 limit = 1;
  int32 offset = 2;
}

message ListActiveRoomsResponse {
  repeated VoiceRoomProto rooms = 1;
  int32 total = 2;
}

message GetCallHistoryRequest {
  string user_id = 1;
  int32 limit = 2;
  int32 offset = 3;
}

message GetCallHistoryResponse {
  repeated VoiceSessionProto sessions = 1;
}

message VoiceSessionProto {
  string id = 1;
  string room_id = 2;
  string user_id = 3;
  string joined_at = 4;
  optional string left_at = 5;
  int32 duration_seconds = 6;
  string session_status = 7;
}
```

